THE GAME
--------

  'PyramiSol' is a solitaire type of game, gameplay is the same as
that of 'Tri-Peaks', 'Golf' or other similar games. In this game,
the board consists of 28 cards that are placed in a triangular
shape. A card (the 'next' card), facing up is shown at the bottom
under the game board. At the left of that card is a pack of the
remaining cards and that pack is face down.

  The goal of the game is to empty all the game board by clicking
on cards that are higher or lower by one unit than the 'next card'
in the bottom of the window. For example, if the card is a 7 of 
Heart, the choosen card should be a 6 or 8, the colour or type of
figure has no importance. Please note that in this game, a King can
follow an Ace or vise versa.

  Have fun!

